Plus sum over i, e to the minus
Ei over kT over Q. Times

00:17:56.190 --> 00:17:56.430
log

00:17:56.430 --> 00:17:59.920
Q. OK good.

00:17:59.920 --> 00:18:01.830
I'm going to take these
summations.

00:18:01.830 --> 00:18:03.340
Now everything is over
