E to the minus Ei over
kT divided by

00:18:07.705 --> 00:18:08.500
the partition function.

00:18:08.500 --> 00:18:09.364
That appears in both.

00:18:09.364 --> 00:18:12.740
I can factor that out. and.

00:18:12.740 --> 00:18:14.360
Then I have these two logs.

00:18:14.360 --> 00:18:18.390
Log of this and log of that.

00:18:18.390 --> 00:18:20.800
That I can also combine
