00:18:35.190 --> 00:18:41.430
S over k is equal to minus Ei.

00:18:41.430 --> 00:18:48.280
Taking the summation out. e to
the minus Ei over kT, over Q.

00:18:48.280 --> 00:18:50.710
That's this term.

00:18:50.710 --> 00:18:52.440
That term.

00:18:52.440 --> 00:18:55.210
And then I have the logs.

00:18:55.210 --> 00:18:58.740
Log of e to the minus
Ei over kT.

00:18:58.740 --> 00:19:00.520
This is a minus sign.

