00:19:08.170 --> 00:19:08.740
Look.

00:19:08.740 --> 00:19:11.520
This e to the minus Ei over kT
over Q. e to the minus Ei over

00:19:11.520 --> 00:19:13.690
kT over Q. What is that?

00:19:13.690 --> 00:19:19.320
That's just pi.

00:19:19.320 --> 00:19:20.710
This is pi.

00:19:20.710 --> 00:19:25.900
That's the probability
of microstate i.

00:19:25.900 --> 00:19:40.390
And this is equal to minus
